PROCESS-NAME,msedge,PROXY,DOMAIN-SUFFIX,edgeservices.bing.com
PROCESS-NAME,msedge,PROXY,DOMAIN-SUFFIX,copilot.microsoft.com
PROCESS-NAME,msedge,PROXY,DOMAIN-SUFFIX,edge.microsoft.com
PROCESS-NAME,msedge,PROXY,DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chatgpt.microsoft.com
PROCESS-NAME,msedge,PROXY,DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ai.microsoft.com

